<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/492822-does-anybody-know-if-there-is-a-way-to">Does anybody know if there is a way to request one of the versions of this book in particular? I know there are two different sequences and I wanted to purchase 2 copies of each version for my library&#39;s book club so they will have equal chance the two different readings. But I am not sure if there is somewhere that I can order it like that...</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_492822'><a id="like_count_community_question_492822" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/492822?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">2 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F20439328-how-to-be-both">like</a></span>

</li>
