        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1175060475" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1765778996410362024">Well, I tried. It won the Booker Prize and had loads of rave reviews, so it must be good, right? Well I read the first half (about George) and it was okay maybe, with reservations because of the odd &amp; difficult-to-understand word usage/style. Then I started the second section and decided that life is just too short and I have way too many books on my &quot;To Read&quot; list anyway. Perhaps Ali Smith is an amazing writer who&apos;s invented a totally new way to write a novel, but it sure didn&apos;t touch me.</span>
  <span id="freeText1765778996410362024" style="display:none">Well, I tried. It won the Booker Prize and had loads of rave reviews, so it must be good, right? Well I read the first half (about George) and it was okay maybe, with reservations because of the odd &amp; difficult-to-understand word usage/style. Then I started the second section and decided that life is just too short and I have way too many books on my "To Read" list anyway. Perhaps Ali Smith is an amazing writer who's invented a totally new way to write a novel, but it sure didn't touch me.</span>
